University of North Carolina Herbarium (NCU)
Mordecai E. Hyams was based in Statesville, NC,
and collected widely in North Carolina. The
"Statesville" on the label should not be taken
as a collecting locality. Plants so labeled are
probably from North Carolina, but no more
definite locality can be determined.
